r‚ÜêStatus req
‚çù Return profiling status information
r‚Üê''   ‚çù Default empty payload
‚çù FIXME empty payload or no payload for 204?
:Select 1‚éïC req.Method
    :Case 'GET'
        r‚Üêstatus
    :Case 'PUT'
        req.Fail 204   ‚çù No Content, can retrieve status with GET
        (q v)‚Üê‚Üì‚çâreq.QueryParams
        new‚Üê(v,‚äÇ'')[q‚ç≥‚äÇ'on']
        :If new‚â°status.on
            :Return
        :ElseIf new‚â°‚äÇ'true'
            status.on‚Üê‚äÇ'true'
            ‚éïPROFILE'start'
        :ElseIf new‚â°‚äÇ'false'
            status.on‚Üê‚äÇ'false'
            ‚éïPROFILE'stop'
        :Else
            req.Fail 400   ‚çù Bad Request
        :EndIf
        status.since‚Üê‚äÉISODateTime ‚éïTS
        r‚Üê''
    :Else
        req.Fail 405   ‚çù Method Not Allowed
:EndSelect
